title: Blackjack Winner Secrets
description:
This ebook contains valuable information for Blackjack players, from total beginners to total pro's.

Included are details on how to play Blackjack from scratch, visual instructions, different ways of playing, rule variations, Blackjack Strategy and more.

Also included is a Blackjack Strategy Chart Calculator for you to use during game play.

All in all, this is a must-have ebook on Blackjack.
